1
00:01:25,310 --> 00:01:29,860
[Coroner's Diary]

2
00:01:30,630 --> 00:01:33,940
[Episode 19]

3
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:38,490
Thank you.

4
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:40,050
You're welcome.

5
00:01:43,930 --> 00:01:45,479
It's all Qing's fault for overreacting.

6
00:01:45,479 --> 00:01:48,009
It's just a minor chill. How could I
trouble you with this, Miss Qin?

7
00:01:48,009 --> 00:01:50,009
As a physician, it's my duty
to heal and save lives.

8
00:01:50,009 --> 00:01:52,210
There's no need to overthink it, Madam.

9
00:01:58,960 --> 00:02:00,320
If you don't mind, Miss Qin,

10
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:01,510
[Mrs. Pang]

11
00:02:00,350 --> 00:02:01,950
just take my pulse like this.

12
00:02:06,150 --> 00:02:07,020
Come on.

13
00:02:08,310 --> 00:02:09,370
Have another bite.

14
00:02:12,790 --> 00:02:15,050
Madam, you truly care about Miss Jia Yun.

15
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:16,510
With such kindness in your heart,

16
00:02:16,510 --> 00:02:18,360
you're sure to be rewarded with blessings
in the future.

17
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,520
Thank you, Miss Qin.

18
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:21,840
Yun and Yan are both well-behaved.

19
00:02:24,050 --> 00:02:26,180
Madam, please give me your other hand.

20
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,240
Who did this to you?

21
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:36,650
I bumped it myself.

22
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,360
Mother is lying.

23
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:40,950
It was Father who hit her.

24
00:02:40,980 --> 00:02:41,950
Don't cry, Yan.

25
00:02:42,870 --> 00:02:43,800
Be good.

26
00:02:45,660 --> 00:02:47,660
Go play in the courtyard for a while.

27
00:02:47,900 --> 00:02:48,700
Be careful.

28
00:02:51,700 --> 00:02:53,380
Madam, these external injuries

29
00:02:53,380 --> 00:02:54,710
only need some ointment

30
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:57,020
and a few days of rest to heal completely.

31
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,880
Thank you, Miss Qin.

32
00:02:58,900 --> 00:03:00,470
However, Madam, you're mentally drained

33
00:03:00,470 --> 00:03:01,730
and have lost all hope.

34
00:03:01,820 --> 00:03:04,480
That is the true root
of your physical weakness.

35
00:03:05,590 --> 00:03:06,440
Miss Qin.

36
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,000
Please help Madam.

37
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:08,520
Qing.

38
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:10,370
-Please get up, Qing.
-Please listen to me.

39
00:03:10,370 --> 00:03:12,530
Master has become
increasingly irritable lately,

40
00:03:12,530 --> 00:03:14,370
taking his frustration out on Madam
at the slightest provocation.

41
00:03:14,370 --> 00:03:15,370
A few days ago,

42
00:03:15,590 --> 00:03:18,190
he called Madam to his study
and tormented her.

43
00:03:18,350 --> 00:03:20,180
The day before yesterday,
Young Master Yan got beaten,

44
00:03:20,180 --> 00:03:22,180
and Master blamed it on Madam again.

45
00:03:22,430 --> 00:03:23,360
You wretch!

46
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,680
If you hadn't been so permissive,

47
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:26,240
would he have stayed out all night?

48
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,400
If you weren't so incompetent,

49
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:29,360
would he have fallen into someone's trap?

50
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,360
I'll beat you to death!

51
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,470
Don't hit my mother!

52
00:03:34,660 --> 00:03:35,980
Mother!

53
00:03:38,079 --> 00:03:39,840
Don't hit Mother!

54
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,590
Mother!

55
00:03:42,870 --> 00:03:44,840
Mother!

56
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:47,910
Stop!

57
00:03:48,820 --> 00:03:50,700
Don't hit Mother!

58
00:03:51,630 --> 00:03:53,000
Mother!

59
00:03:54,060 --> 00:03:55,620
Madam cries every day

60
00:03:55,980 --> 00:03:57,180
and can't eat a thing.

61
00:03:57,630 --> 00:03:59,890
How could she not feel utterly hopeless?

62
00:03:59,990 --> 00:04:00,710
Qing.

63
00:04:00,730 --> 00:04:01,860
-Miss Qin.
-Come on.

64
00:04:01,950 --> 00:04:03,560
Please help Madam.

65
00:04:03,870 --> 00:04:04,700
I beg you.

66
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:07,000
Mother, I'm hungry.

67
00:04:10,110 --> 00:04:10,790
Qing.

68
00:04:11,150 --> 00:04:12,810
Don't make things hard for Miss Qin.

69
00:04:12,810 --> 00:04:14,020
Go feed Yun.

70
00:04:17,050 --> 00:04:17,930
Come on.

71
00:04:22,490 --> 00:04:23,330
Come on.

72
00:04:28,990 --> 00:04:30,370
When I first met Yun,

73
00:04:30,730 --> 00:04:31,850
she was like this—

74
00:04:33,070 --> 00:04:35,870
always acting like
a four or five-year-old child.

75
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:39,330
Madam, with your two children,

76
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:41,490
what do you plan to do in the future?

77
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:43,670
Though my husband treats me indifferently,

78
00:04:43,670 --> 00:04:45,480
he dotes on Yan greatly.

79
00:04:46,310 --> 00:04:47,590
When Yan grows up a bit,

80
00:04:47,950 --> 00:04:50,100
he can help his father
uphold the family name,

81
00:04:50,100 --> 00:04:51,120
and perhaps things will get better then.

82
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:53,170
Madam,
please don't harbor any more illusions.

83
00:04:53,170 --> 00:04:54,840
If a man can hit you once,

84
00:04:54,909 --> 00:04:56,430
he will do it countless times.

85
00:04:56,430 --> 00:04:58,070
He'll only become
more and more comfortable

86
00:04:58,070 --> 00:04:59,360
and reckless with it.

87
00:04:59,630 --> 00:05:01,480
Men who raise their hands against women

88
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,560
are all of corrupt character,

89
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:04,160
complete and utter cowards.

90
00:05:04,300 --> 00:05:05,180
How could they possibly have

91
00:05:05,180 --> 00:05:07,840
the willpower and determination
to change themselves?

92
00:05:07,840 --> 00:05:09,440
I don't expect him to change.

93
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:12,570
I just hope Yan can grow up quickly.

94
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:14,360
What difference will it make
when he grows up?

95
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,910
Watching his mother be humiliated

96
00:05:15,910 --> 00:05:17,940
and abused every day,
powerless to do anything.

97
00:05:17,940 --> 00:05:19,150
Over time,

98
00:05:19,350 --> 00:05:21,300
that will only leave him full of
resentment and repression.

99
00:05:21,300 --> 00:05:22,360
How could he possibly grow into

100
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:24,040
someone strong and responsible?

101
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:26,970
Madam, please stop
using your children as an excuse.

102
00:05:30,810 --> 00:05:32,470
Miss Qin, everything you said

103
00:05:33,190 --> 00:05:34,630
is wise and kind.

104
00:05:35,930 --> 00:05:37,190
It's just that for now,

105
00:05:37,270 --> 00:05:38,560
I can still manage.

106
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:41,420
I think I'll endure it for the time being.

107
00:05:41,420 --> 00:05:44,240
Madam, if you don't want
to live in this hell forever,

108
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:46,510
you have no choice but to risk everything
and leave this all behind.

109
00:05:46,510 --> 00:05:50,240
Only then will you and your children
have a chance for a better life.

110
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,880
I, Qin Wan, have said all I can.

111
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:54,409
I hope you will consider it carefully,
Madam.

112
00:06:02,440 --> 00:06:03,360
Miss Qin.

113
00:06:04,330 --> 00:06:06,990
Please don't blame Madam
for being indecisive.

114
00:06:07,350 --> 00:06:09,140
Her family is also in business.

115
00:06:10,100 --> 00:06:11,220
Years ago,

116
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:13,300
to acquire Madam's family's assets,

117
00:06:13,700 --> 00:06:14,830
Master conspired with others,

118
00:06:14,830 --> 00:06:15,680
forcing her family

119
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:17,190
to the brink of ruin.

120
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:20,190
To protect her family business,

121
00:06:20,450 --> 00:06:23,180
Madam reluctantly became
Master's second wife.

122
00:06:23,370 --> 00:06:24,720
So Madam's family was willing

123
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:26,330
to sacrifice their daughter's life

124
00:06:26,330 --> 00:06:27,930
just to save their business?

125
00:06:28,030 --> 00:06:29,720
If her family business collapsed,

126
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:31,580
Madam would have no way out at all.

127
00:06:32,190 --> 00:06:34,240
Besides, she has two children.

128
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:37,370
If she really left the Pang family
for her own sake,

129
00:06:37,370 --> 00:06:39,750
Young Master Jia Yan
would lose everything,

130
00:06:39,750 --> 00:06:42,170
and all these years of her endurance
would be for nothing.

131
00:06:42,170 --> 00:06:43,900
Miss Qin, you're a nice person,

132
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:45,360
but

133
00:06:46,190 --> 00:06:47,830
if you haven't experienced
someone else's pain,

134
00:06:47,830 --> 00:06:49,390
perhaps don't be too quick to judge.

135
00:06:49,390 --> 00:06:51,120
Madam is not like you, Miss Qin.

136
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:53,000
She doesn't have skills to rely on,

137
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,659
so she can only submit to fate.

138
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,680
In this world,

139
00:06:58,340 --> 00:06:59,420
facing injustice,

140
00:07:00,370 --> 00:07:02,690
what can a powerless woman do

141
00:07:03,780 --> 00:07:05,040
but endure it quietly?

142
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:10,660
The relationship
between Qing Yun, Liu Renli,

143
00:07:10,660 --> 00:07:12,990
and Pang Fuliang is truly extraordinary.

144
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,920
The Shuangqing Troupe travels
far and wide,

145
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,200
making the world their home.

146
00:07:16,200 --> 00:07:18,010
But Qing Yun, just to see them,

147
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:19,570
travels thousands of miles

148
00:07:19,670 --> 00:07:21,070
to Yuzhou almost every year

149
00:07:21,070 --> 00:07:23,040
for a reunion.

150
00:07:23,310 --> 00:07:24,930
Even ordinary relatives

151
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:26,930
aren't this close.

152
00:07:28,540 --> 00:07:30,430
Pang Fuliang is quite generous too.

153
00:07:30,430 --> 00:07:32,390
Wherever there's a Shifang Inn,

154
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:35,159
it's always available
for the Shuangqing Troupe.

155
00:07:35,159 --> 00:07:37,120
The Shuangqing Troupe's fame
across the land

156
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,280
owes much to

157
00:07:38,750 --> 00:07:40,150
Pang Fuliang's support.

158
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:43,020
What special talent do you think
Qing Yun has

159
00:07:43,200 --> 00:07:45,600
that makes Pang Fuliang
so generous to her?

160
00:07:46,470 --> 00:07:47,150
Chi.

161
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:49,560
You've hit on something important.

162
00:07:49,950 --> 00:07:52,530
Do you know
why Liu Renli remains unmarried?

163
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:57,270
As they say,
the falling flower has feelings,

164
00:07:57,409 --> 00:07:59,190
-but the flowing water is indifferent.
-Just say it.

165
00:07:59,190 --> 00:08:00,200
Look at you,

166
00:08:00,410 --> 00:08:02,340
you have no sense of romance at all.

167
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,990
Liu Renli is deeply in love with Qing Yun,

168
00:08:04,990 --> 00:08:06,950
but she doesn't care for him at all.

169
00:08:08,550 --> 00:08:09,960
Are you saying

170
00:08:09,980 --> 00:08:12,310
Pang Fuliang is only
being nice to Qing Yun

171
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,690
to win Liu Renli over?

172
00:08:13,710 --> 00:08:14,510
Exactly.

173
00:08:14,540 --> 00:08:15,210
Master,

174
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:17,100
there's new information.

175
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:20,640
Qing Yun, Liu Renli, and Pang Fuliang

176
00:08:20,670 --> 00:08:21,870
are indeed all from Dingzhou.

177
00:08:21,870 --> 00:08:23,530
Liu Renli used to run
a martial arts school in Dingzhou.

178
00:08:23,530 --> 00:08:24,780
Later, the three of them left together,

179
00:08:24,780 --> 00:08:25,690
and only Qing Yun returned

180
00:08:25,690 --> 00:08:28,120
to Dingzhou to retire
under the name Madam Qin.

181
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,870
When they left Dingzhou,

182
00:08:30,670 --> 00:08:33,070
a major gold heist
had just occurred there.

183
00:08:33,880 --> 00:08:35,240
A gold heist?

184
00:08:35,669 --> 00:08:36,919
How much gold was stolen?

185
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:38,280
Was it real gold or paper money?

186
00:08:38,280 --> 00:08:39,549
Have they caught the bandits?

187
00:08:39,549 --> 00:08:42,280
How come I never heard of
such a sensational case?

188
00:08:45,470 --> 00:08:47,360
It was an unsolved case from 15 years ago.

189
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,880
Since it involved stolen military funds,

190
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:50,400
His Majesty had it covered up.

191
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:51,670
I only know because I overheard Father

192
00:08:51,670 --> 00:08:53,800
discussing it with his subordinates.

193
00:08:54,550 --> 00:08:56,410
I never expected Qing Yun's death

194
00:08:56,470 --> 00:08:58,670
would be connected to such a major case.

195
00:09:00,160 --> 00:09:01,350
Chi, do you suspect

196
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:02,970
they were behind it?

197
00:09:04,190 --> 00:09:06,120
You two, come with me to the prison.

198
00:09:06,450 --> 00:09:08,450
It's time to interrogate Yang Ying.

199
00:09:20,270 --> 00:09:21,130
Little Wan'er!

200
00:09:21,890 --> 00:09:23,350
I knew you're still awake.

201
00:09:24,420 --> 00:09:26,710
Do you know what I've been doing
these past few days?

202
00:09:26,710 --> 00:09:27,390
No idea.

203
00:09:29,550 --> 00:09:32,270
Yan Li and I went undercover,

204
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:34,360
as spies.

205
00:09:35,550 --> 00:09:36,300
Was it fun?

206
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:37,790
Fun? Not at all.

207
00:09:38,290 --> 00:09:39,950
We discovered something big.

208
00:09:40,310 --> 00:09:42,840
That Pang fellow is definitely
not a good guy.

209
00:09:45,580 --> 00:09:47,130
My Lady, Your Highness.

210
00:09:48,950 --> 00:09:49,920
Young Master Yan says

211
00:09:49,920 --> 00:09:51,160
we need to pack our belongings quickly

212
00:09:51,160 --> 00:09:53,490
and leave Yuzhou early tomorrow morning.

213
00:09:53,670 --> 00:09:54,880
Why such a hurry?

214
00:09:54,880 --> 00:09:56,040
Does Chi know about this?

215
00:09:56,040 --> 00:09:56,900
No, he doesn't.

216
00:09:57,550 --> 00:09:58,350
No need to ask.

217
00:09:58,830 --> 00:10:00,920
It must be related to Liu Renli's death.

218
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:02,160
Go pack our things first.

219
00:10:02,160 --> 00:10:03,640
Ning and I will make a run
to the prefect's office.

220
00:10:03,640 --> 00:10:04,120
Okay.

221
00:10:04,430 --> 00:10:10,270
♪ The Dharma sees
the child's filial piety ♪

222
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:17,790
♪ He tries to find
and save his mother in hell ♪

223
00:10:17,790 --> 00:10:20,920
♪ Ride on the auspicious cloud,
heading for Mount Lingshan ♪

224
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:22,880
Every time I hear this part,

225
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:24,240
someone dies.

226
00:10:27,070 --> 00:10:29,550
This is already the fourth time
I've heard it.

227
00:10:29,550 --> 00:10:33,550
♪ Buddha's compassion ♪

228
00:10:33,550 --> 00:10:40,310
♪ Guides the way ♪

229
00:10:44,730 --> 00:10:46,130
Why did she stop singing?

230
00:10:48,640 --> 00:10:49,240
Let's go.

231
00:11:47,550 --> 00:11:48,810
What's wrong with her?

232
00:11:49,040 --> 00:11:49,950
She probably had a seizure.

233
00:11:49,950 --> 00:11:51,550
She got frightened just now.

234
00:11:51,690 --> 00:11:52,360
Come on.

235
00:12:08,920 --> 00:12:09,710
Yang Ying.

236
00:12:10,520 --> 00:12:12,470
Since its founding, the Shuangqing Troupe

237
00:12:12,470 --> 00:12:14,400
has always had two leaders.

238
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:17,220
Why is it that after Qing Yun left,

239
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:19,040
the number of leaders
went from two to one?

240
00:12:19,040 --> 00:12:19,970
That's not true.

241
00:12:20,070 --> 00:12:22,160
There was another leader, Qingxi.

242
00:12:22,590 --> 00:12:23,990
She's Qing Yun's junior,

243
00:12:24,310 --> 00:12:25,670
but later she got married

244
00:12:25,670 --> 00:12:27,120
and left with her apprentice.

245
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:29,360
Qing Yun had a falling out
with her after that.

246
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:31,280
What was Qingxi's apprentice's name?

247
00:12:31,280 --> 00:12:32,280
Qing Huan.

248
00:12:32,670 --> 00:12:35,000
In terms of movement techniques
and vocal skills,

249
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:37,940
she's better than
Qing Yun's apprentice Qing Li.

250
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:39,420
It's really a pity.

251
00:12:39,950 --> 00:12:41,540
And who did Qingxi marry?

252
00:12:42,280 --> 00:12:44,190
A general from the Northwest,

253
00:12:44,520 --> 00:12:46,050
surnamed Zhang, I believe.

254
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:49,760
He also helped her
escape her lowly status.

255
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:56,700
So when did Leader Qing Yun

256
00:12:57,040 --> 00:12:58,770
pass her position

257
00:12:59,040 --> 00:13:00,190
to Qing Li?

258
00:13:00,760 --> 00:13:01,640
About

259
00:13:01,950 --> 00:13:03,750
eight or nine years ago, I think.

260
00:13:04,190 --> 00:13:06,160
After Leader Qingxi got married,

261
00:13:06,160 --> 00:13:07,590
Qing Yun drank every day

262
00:13:07,590 --> 00:13:09,790
and lost interest
in managing the Shuangqing Troupe.

263
00:13:09,790 --> 00:13:11,000
15 years ago,

264
00:13:11,310 --> 00:13:13,830
Qing Yun followed Mr. Pang
to do business in the Northwest

265
00:13:13,830 --> 00:13:15,000
and made a fortune.

266
00:13:15,640 --> 00:13:16,480
Later,

267
00:13:16,710 --> 00:13:20,290
it was said that Leader Qingxi
took her disciples to visit her hometown

268
00:13:20,290 --> 00:13:21,850
and was killed by bandits.

269
00:13:22,400 --> 00:13:23,430
After that,

270
00:13:23,950 --> 00:13:26,670
Qing Yun handed over the leadership
to Qing Li

271
00:13:26,950 --> 00:13:28,430
and retired herself.

272
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:30,240
Occasionally after that,

