00:28:38,400 --> 00:28:41,190
none should have died unjustly and without
clear cause due to vigilante punishment.

547
00:28:41,190 --> 00:28:42,270
Such revenge

548
00:28:42,510 --> 00:28:44,560
neither serves as a warning to the public

549
00:28:44,560 --> 00:28:46,710
nor honors
General Zhang's noble reputation.

550
00:28:46,710 --> 00:28:47,970
No matter the reasons,

551
00:28:48,160 --> 00:28:50,190
the criminals' crimes
should be made public

552
00:28:50,190 --> 00:28:52,390
and then punished according to the law,

553
00:28:52,600 --> 00:28:53,560
including those

554
00:28:54,030 --> 00:28:55,470
who deserve to die.

555
00:28:55,470 --> 00:28:56,270
Rest assured.

556
00:28:57,320 --> 00:28:58,920
We'll definitely bring the gold heist

557
00:28:58,920 --> 00:29:00,030
back to light

558
00:29:00,470 --> 00:29:01,290
and use the law

559
00:29:01,990 --> 00:29:03,750
to give General Zhang the justice
he deserved.

560
00:29:03,620 --> 00:29:05,210
[Autopsy Form]

561
00:29:06,080 --> 00:29:06,640
Madam.

562
00:29:06,640 --> 00:29:08,430
Governor Wang has surrounded
our courtyard with his men,

563
00:29:08,430 --> 00:29:10,560
saying they're here to make an arrest.

564
00:29:12,560 --> 00:29:15,800
Qing, you're suspected of
murdering Pang Fuliang

565
00:29:15,800 --> 00:29:17,800
and burning his body to destroy evidence.

566
00:29:17,800 --> 00:29:19,800
You are to be arrested immediately.

567
00:29:19,840 --> 00:29:21,560
Qing couldn't possibly do such a thing.

568
00:29:21,560 --> 00:29:22,950
I'll go with them.

569
00:29:33,430 --> 00:29:34,950
What's wrong, Qing?

570
00:29:37,030 --> 00:29:38,630
It's nothing, Young Master.

571
00:29:39,880 --> 00:29:40,410
Be good.

572
00:29:45,900 --> 00:29:46,690
Madam.

573
00:29:47,270 --> 00:29:48,190
From now on,

574
00:29:48,190 --> 00:29:49,850
Young Master and Eldest Madam

575
00:29:49,880 --> 00:29:51,540
will be entirely in your care.

576
00:30:04,470 --> 00:30:05,930
-Qing!
-Yan.

577
00:30:06,080 --> 00:30:07,950
On what grounds are you arresting Qing?

578
00:30:07,950 --> 00:30:10,400
-Yan.
-Don't you mistreat Qing!

579
00:30:11,130 --> 00:30:15,180
♪ Little child, playing hide and seek ♪

580
00:30:15,670 --> 00:30:20,230
♪ Behind the table, grinning ♪

581
00:30:24,410 --> 00:30:26,570
Qing, where are you going?

582
00:30:26,600 --> 00:30:28,160
Come play with me.

583
00:30:28,450 --> 00:30:30,170
Qing, don't leave!

584
00:30:31,020 --> 00:30:32,700
-Qing!
-Qing!

585
00:30:34,920 --> 00:30:36,360
Court is in session.

586
00:30:39,950 --> 00:30:41,550
Who stands before the court?

587
00:30:41,880 --> 00:30:43,120
State your name.

588
00:30:43,710 --> 00:30:45,570
I am

589
00:30:45,840 --> 00:30:47,030
Qing, maid of the Pang household.

590
00:30:47,030 --> 00:30:48,750
Surveillance Commissioner Yan Chi

591
00:30:48,750 --> 00:30:50,510
has accused a member of
the Shuangqing Troupe,

592
00:30:50,510 --> 00:30:52,320
Qing Huan, a disciple of Qingxi,

593
00:30:52,320 --> 00:30:56,400
of murdering the former Shuangqing Troupe
Leader Qing Yun,

594
00:30:56,400 --> 00:31:00,080
Troupe Leader Qing Li, Jianghuai Circuit
Transport Commissioner Liu Renli,

595
00:31:00,080 --> 00:31:02,360
and Pang Fuliang,
a gentry from Yuzhou, for revenge.

596
00:31:02,360 --> 00:31:03,430
So many people?

597
00:31:03,430 --> 00:31:04,840
She killed so many people.
That's four already.

598
00:31:04,840 --> 00:31:05,670
How cruel.

599
00:31:05,670 --> 00:31:06,950
But she looks like a powerless woman.

600
00:31:06,950 --> 00:31:07,970
The one kneeling—

601
00:31:08,360 --> 00:31:10,120
are you Qing Huan,

602
00:31:10,120 --> 00:31:11,560
now known as Qing?

603
00:31:12,080 --> 00:31:13,970
I'm now simply Qing.

604
00:31:14,820 --> 00:31:17,340
Do you admit to the accusations

605
00:31:17,360 --> 00:31:18,620
just made against you?

606
00:31:18,800 --> 00:31:20,460
There's no proof or evidence.

607
00:31:20,600 --> 00:31:21,530
I do not admit it.

608
00:31:22,920 --> 00:31:26,650
Commissioner Yan, do you have any evidence
to present to the court?

609
00:31:27,190 --> 00:31:28,590
I request my strategist,

610
00:31:28,750 --> 00:31:30,150
Qin Wan, to come forward.

611
00:31:30,510 --> 00:31:31,290
Summon.

612
00:31:31,560 --> 00:31:33,920
Summoning Qin Wan to the court!

613
00:31:41,820 --> 00:31:42,860
I am Qin Wan.

614
00:31:44,530 --> 00:31:46,060
Greetings, Governor Wang.

615
00:31:46,600 --> 00:31:48,260
Master Wan, please rise.

616
00:31:49,190 --> 00:31:50,390
Thank you, Governor.

617
00:31:51,030 --> 00:31:54,090
However, my evidence
is rather extensive and complex.

618
00:31:54,190 --> 00:31:55,800
Since Qing has not yet been convicted,

619
00:31:55,800 --> 00:31:58,860
may I ask if you would allow her to stand,
Governor Wang?

620
00:32:05,600 --> 00:32:06,400
You may rise.

621
00:32:06,670 --> 00:32:08,130
Thank you, Governor Wang.

622
00:32:10,270 --> 00:32:13,430
Master Wan, do you have evidence
to present to the court?

623
00:32:16,880 --> 00:32:17,840
Bring a table.

624
00:32:29,710 --> 00:32:30,750
These two arrows—

625
00:32:31,030 --> 00:32:32,990
one has a wooden shaft with an iron tip,

626
00:32:32,990 --> 00:32:34,880
the other is made entirely of iron.

627
00:32:34,880 --> 00:32:36,160
This pure iron arrow

628
00:32:36,160 --> 00:32:38,880
was removed from the victim's body
as the murder weapon.

629
00:32:38,880 --> 00:32:40,410
And this iron-tipped arrow

630
00:32:40,430 --> 00:32:43,600
is the one originally included
in the quiver for performance use.

631
00:32:43,600 --> 00:32:45,510
The killer replaced this iron-tipped arrow

632
00:32:45,510 --> 00:32:46,910
with a pure iron one,

633
00:32:47,090 --> 00:32:48,420
increasing the weight,

634
00:32:48,430 --> 00:32:51,030
requiring the mechanism to be triggered
twice in succession to release it.

635
00:32:51,030 --> 00:32:53,510
Therefore, when Yang Ying
lowered her head again,

636
00:32:53,510 --> 00:32:54,600
the iron arrow was released

637
00:32:54,600 --> 00:32:56,270
and struck the victim's vital point.

638
00:32:56,270 --> 00:32:57,270
The first victim,

639
00:32:57,270 --> 00:33:00,400
Qing Li, died from an arrow shot
during the performance.

640
00:33:00,840 --> 00:33:02,710
I see now.

641
00:33:02,710 --> 00:33:04,770
Please pass all of these
to Governor.

642
00:33:08,470 --> 00:33:09,670
Governor, please take a look.

643
00:33:09,670 --> 00:33:11,190
These are the postmortem report

644
00:33:11,190 --> 00:33:12,830
and the crime scene sketches

645
00:33:12,860 --> 00:33:14,410
[Postmortem Report]

646
00:33:13,030 --> 00:33:14,830
of the second victim, Madam Qin.

647
00:33:15,190 --> 00:33:16,470
The white bottle contains

648
00:33:16,470 --> 00:33:18,880
powdered Datura seeds found
in the victim's stomach,

649
00:33:18,880 --> 00:33:20,210
and the sachet contains

650
00:33:20,270 --> 00:33:21,640
Datura fruit grown

651
00:33:21,640 --> 00:33:24,220
by the suspect Qing at her residence.

652
00:33:27,060 --> 00:33:29,190
The Shuangqing Troupe Leader Qing Yun,

653
00:33:29,190 --> 00:33:30,650
using her alias Madam Qin,

654
00:33:31,120 --> 00:33:33,080
had a private conversation
with Pang Fuliang in his study,

655
00:33:33,080 --> 00:33:35,080
demanding the Shifang Inn from him.

656
00:33:35,460 --> 00:33:38,260
They had a heated argument
and parted on bad terms.

657
00:33:38,640 --> 00:33:40,750
The killer knew
Madam Qin was fond of drinking,

658
00:33:40,750 --> 00:33:41,990
so they took the opportunity

659
00:33:41,990 --> 00:33:44,050
to put Datura seed powder in her wine.

660
00:33:44,120 --> 00:33:46,360
After Madam Qin passed out
due to the poison,

661
00:33:46,360 --> 00:33:48,030
the suspect snuck into her room,

662
00:33:48,030 --> 00:33:49,920
removed Madam Qin's waistband,

663
00:33:49,920 --> 00:33:51,710
dragged her near the beam,

664
00:33:51,990 --> 00:33:53,080
and used a hemp rope

665
00:33:53,080 --> 00:33:55,360
to hang Madam Qin from the beam.

666
00:33:55,360 --> 00:33:58,640
Then the waistband
was looped over the beam

667
00:33:58,640 --> 00:34:00,470
and tied around Madam Qin's neck,

668
00:34:00,470 --> 00:34:02,600
after which the hemp rope
around her waist was untied,

669
00:34:02,600 --> 00:34:05,930
using the falling body's momentum
to strangle her to death.

670
00:34:22,239 --> 00:34:23,909
Jumping onto the beam

671
00:34:24,320 --> 00:34:26,400
is not something
an ordinary person could do.

672
00:34:26,400 --> 00:34:28,280
How did Qing manage it?

673
00:34:29,320 --> 00:34:33,520
This is the testimony of Yang Ying,
deputy leader of the Shuangqing Troupe.

674
00:34:38,630 --> 00:34:39,530
Qing

675
00:34:39,980 --> 00:34:41,239
is actually Qing Huan.

676
00:34:41,590 --> 00:34:43,840
She fully inherited
her master Qingxi's skills.

677
00:34:43,840 --> 00:34:45,989
Her singing skills, lightness techniques,
and movement techniques

678
00:34:45,989 --> 00:34:47,920
are all outstanding among her peers.

679
00:34:47,920 --> 00:34:50,070
Even the Shuangqing Troupe Leader Qing Li

680
00:34:50,070 --> 00:34:51,730
was slightly inferior to her.

681
00:34:55,850 --> 00:34:56,739
Qing.

682
00:34:57,880 --> 00:34:58,720
Do you admit

683
00:34:59,070 --> 00:35:00,950
to what Commissioner Yan

684
00:35:00,950 --> 00:35:02,240
just stated?

685
00:35:08,720 --> 00:35:09,680
I admit it.

686
00:35:15,110 --> 00:35:16,260
She killed so many people!

687
00:35:16,260 --> 00:35:18,260
How could she bring herself to do it?

688
00:35:19,180 --> 00:35:20,190
Silence!

689
00:35:20,950 --> 00:35:21,860
Master Wan.

690
00:35:22,320 --> 00:35:25,250
Do you have any more evidence
to present to the court?

691
00:35:25,990 --> 00:35:27,450
No need for more evidence.

692
00:35:30,430 --> 00:35:31,570
I killed them all.

693
00:35:32,390 --> 00:35:34,190
It was me who shot Qing Li,

694
00:35:34,510 --> 00:35:35,580
hanged Qing Yun,

695
00:35:36,240 --> 00:35:37,470
drowned Liu Renli,

696
00:35:37,470 --> 00:35:40,820
and stabbed Pang Fuliang to death,
burning his body afterwards.

697
00:35:40,820 --> 00:35:42,220
No one else was involved.

698
00:35:46,630 --> 00:35:47,920
This is too vicious.

699
00:35:47,920 --> 00:35:48,800
This is a blatant disregard
for the law!

700
00:35:48,800 --> 00:35:50,680
She deserves to be executed!
Truly inhuman!

701
00:35:50,680 --> 00:35:51,630
Qing,

702
00:35:51,990 --> 00:35:54,650
are you confessing to your crimes
here in court?

703
00:35:54,760 --> 00:35:55,630
By the law,

704
00:35:56,400 --> 00:35:57,360
I am guilty;

705
00:35:57,950 --> 00:35:59,350
but by human conscience,

706
00:36:00,400 --> 00:36:01,470
I am innocent.

707
00:36:02,760 --> 00:36:03,840
What?

708
00:36:04,030 --> 00:36:05,990
She claims she's innocent.

709
00:36:09,880 --> 00:36:10,840
Silence!

710
00:36:11,240 --> 00:36:12,640
You insolent woman.

711
00:36:13,110 --> 00:36:14,950
How dare you make a fool of me!

712
00:36:16,720 --> 00:36:17,580
Governor Wang.

713
00:36:18,360 --> 00:36:20,360
I have a few questions for Miss Qing.

714
00:36:20,990 --> 00:36:21,920
Please proceed.

715
00:36:23,800 --> 00:36:24,950
With your skills,

716
00:36:25,520 --> 00:36:27,630
when you stabbed Pang Fuliang
with your sword,

717
00:36:27,630 --> 00:36:29,960
could you have killed him with one strike?

718
00:36:30,840 --> 00:36:31,570
Yes, I could.

719
00:36:32,110 --> 00:36:32,720
Then why did you

720
00:36:32,720 --> 00:36:34,920
deliberately miss his heart by an inch?

721
00:36:34,920 --> 00:36:36,760
Because I wanted him to suffer,

722
00:36:37,150 --> 00:36:39,680
to watch himself being burned alive.

723
00:36:40,360 --> 00:36:42,290
What kind of grudge did you two have

724
00:36:42,400 --> 00:36:44,530
that drove you to harm him so severely?

725
00:36:46,150 --> 00:36:47,110
They were just a bunch of

726
00:36:47,110 --> 00:36:49,380
cold-hearted, rotten, and vicious people.

727
00:36:49,380 --> 00:36:50,270
Because they

728
00:36:50,760 --> 00:36:52,890
conspired to hang my master Qingxi,

729
00:36:53,360 --> 00:36:55,760
shoot General Zhang, my master's husband,

730
00:36:55,950 --> 00:36:58,110
and drown my master's eldest son.

731
00:36:58,110 --> 00:36:59,720
Even my master's little daughter,
Jia Yun,

732
00:36:59,720 --> 00:37:02,120
was frightened into such
a state of idiocy.

733
00:37:03,200 --> 00:37:04,200
Because they

734
00:37:04,820 --> 00:37:06,170
were the real culprits

735
00:37:06,200 --> 00:37:08,400
behind the gold heist from 15 years ago!

736
00:37:08,830 --> 00:37:09,600
What?

737
00:37:09,720 --> 00:37:11,550
This is an earth-shattering secret!

738
00:37:11,550 --> 00:37:13,880
The culprit hasn't been found in 15 years.

739
00:37:23,550 --> 00:37:24,580
Court dismissed!

740
00:37:24,950 --> 00:37:27,360
The gold heist
will be tried another day.

741
00:37:27,750 --> 00:37:29,230
Take Qing away!

742
00:37:40,880 --> 00:37:41,720
Thank you.

743
00:38:08,910 --> 00:38:11,910
Should I call you Qing Huan or Qing?

744
00:38:12,470 --> 00:38:15,270
Since I left the Shuangqing Troupe
with my master,

745
00:38:15,630 --> 00:38:18,690
the name Qing Huan has had
nothing to do with me anymore.

746
00:38:18,780 --> 00:38:20,180
Please just call me Qing.

747
00:38:23,120 --> 00:38:25,450
I presented the evidence and accused you,

748
00:38:25,720 --> 00:38:27,550
yet you hold no grudge against me at all.

749
00:38:27,550 --> 00:38:29,880
From the moment I did those deadly deeds,

750
00:38:30,460 --> 00:38:31,920
I knew this day would come.

751
00:38:32,350 --> 00:38:34,550
Why should I harbor hatred towards you?

752
00:38:35,200 --> 00:38:36,680
Miss Qin, since you were willing

753
00:38:36,680 --> 00:38:39,150
to help me reveal the injustice
from back then in court,

754
00:38:39,150 --> 00:38:41,590
you must have known something
about what happened.

755
00:38:41,590 --> 00:38:43,790
I might as well tell you
the whole truth.

756
00:38:44,200 --> 00:38:47,070
Miss Qin, I believe you'll
understand my intentions.

757
00:38:47,070 --> 00:38:49,280
Though Qing Yun was older than my master,

758
00:38:49,280 --> 00:38:50,630
she was narrow-minded,

759
00:38:50,990 --> 00:38:52,920
envious, and resentful of talent.

760
00:38:52,950 --> 00:38:55,350
She envied my master
for marrying a good man

761
00:38:55,550 --> 00:38:57,950
and coveted the wealth
of the general's household.

762
00:38:57,950 --> 00:38:59,510
Therefore, after falling out
with my master,

763
00:38:59,510 --> 00:39:02,320
she came back,
pretending to rekindle their sisterhood.

764
00:39:02,320 --> 00:39:04,110
My master was very loyal and trusting,

765
00:39:04,110 --> 00:39:06,070
so she was easily fooled
by Qing Yun's act,

766
00:39:06,070 --> 00:39:07,330
which invited trouble

767
00:39:07,630 --> 00:39:09,560
and planted the seeds of disaster.

768
00:39:09,840 --> 00:39:11,880
The journey was going smoothly, and once

769
00:39:11,880 --> 00:39:14,920
we reached Mengzhou, the border troops
were supposed to meet us.

770
00:39:14,920 --> 00:39:17,750
But unexpectedly, Qing Yun colluded with
Pang Fuliang and Liu Renli...

771
00:39:17,750 --> 00:39:18,140
Kill!

772
00:39:18,170 --> 00:39:20,100
Bringing Qing Li to Dingzhou.

773
00:39:20,320 --> 00:39:23,590
They disguised themselves as coachmen
and cooks to sneak into the inn,

774
00:39:23,590 --> 00:39:25,450
drugged the escorting soldiers,

775
00:39:25,720 --> 00:39:26,840
and slaughtered

776
00:39:27,320 --> 00:39:28,510
everyone.

777
00:39:40,360 --> 00:39:42,400
Master's two children

778
00:39:42,400 --> 00:39:44,490
were just innocent little kids back then,

779
00:39:44,490 --> 00:39:46,550
but that vicious wretch

780
00:39:46,840 --> 00:39:49,000
still threw them into the well.

781
00:40:07,400 --> 00:40:09,730
Fortunately, that day, Master advised me

782
00:40:10,720 --> 00:40:12,580
to be more respectful to Qing Yun.

783
00:40:13,110 --> 00:40:14,850
Acting on impulse, I hid away

784
00:40:15,240 --> 00:40:16,300
and thus survived.

785
00:40:17,320 --> 00:40:18,930
So Lady Jia Yun...

786
00:40:19,590 --> 00:40:22,250
Right, Jia Yun was Master's
youngest daughter.

787
00:40:22,470 --> 00:40:23,680
After they left,

788
00:40:24,470 --> 00:40:26,600
I immediately went down into the well.

789
00:40:27,840 --> 00:40:28,760
But

790
00:40:30,920 --> 00:40:32,770
only Jia Yun survived.

791
00:40:34,840 --> 00:40:37,970
Her older brother carried her
on his back until his death

792
00:40:38,880 --> 00:40:40,610
and ended up drowning himself.

793
00:40:43,110 --> 00:40:45,440
That's how Jia Yun ended up
like she is now.

794
00:40:47,510 --> 00:40:48,920
So you did all this

795
00:40:51,240 --> 00:40:54,070
to make Qing Yun and the others
pay blood for blood?

796
00:40:54,920 --> 00:40:56,780
For a lowborn woman like me,

797
00:40:57,760 --> 00:41:00,760
I had to become even more ruthless
than those villains

798
00:41:01,430 --> 00:41:04,320
to seek justice for my master's family.

799
00:41:04,950 --> 00:41:07,070
But why didn't you report it
to the authorities?

800
00:41:07,070 --> 00:41:08,030
Miss Qin.

801
00:41:08,510 --> 00:41:10,800
The gold heist involved military funds.

802
00:41:11,320 --> 00:41:12,360
Have you ever wondered

803
00:41:12,360 --> 00:41:14,720
why it could remain hidden for 15 years?

804
00:41:15,630 --> 00:41:17,690
General Zhang was brave and upright,

805
00:41:17,840 --> 00:41:19,840
and my master was kind and generous.

806
00:41:19,880 --> 00:41:22,760
Why did they die tragically
at the hands of villains,

807
00:41:22,760 --> 00:41:24,840
while those scoundrels could rise to power

808
00:41:24,840 --> 00:41:26,440
and do whatever they please?

809
00:41:27,030 --> 00:41:27,830
In this world,

810
00:41:28,320 --> 00:41:29,880
there's no true justice

811
00:41:29,880 --> 00:41:31,660
or clear distinctions
between right and wrong.

812
00:41:31,660 --> 00:41:33,660
It all comes down to power and money.

813
00:41:34,510 --> 00:41:36,430
True justice,

814
00:41:40,260 --> 00:41:42,920
clear distinctions
between right and wrong...

815
00:41:52,540 --> 00:41:53,260
Wan.

816
00:41:53,430 --> 00:41:55,550
When judging a case, remember:
official matters belong to authorities,

817
00:41:55,550 --> 00:41:58,950
right and wrong have reason,
and severity is governed by law.

818
00:41:59,110 --> 00:42:01,330
One must not override public justice
for personal reasons,

819
00:42:01,330 --> 00:42:03,040
nor bend the law

820
00:42:03,070 --> 00:42:05,000
to favor personal relationships.

821
00:42:09,070 --> 00:42:11,630
The unexceedable bounds
of severity and leniency

822
00:42:11,630 --> 00:42:13,030
constitute the law;

823
00:42:13,950 --> 00:42:16,780
carefully upholding legal principles while
deeply considering human circumstances

824
00:42:16,780 --> 00:42:18,910
is what makes the law strict and clear.

825
00:42:20,240 --> 00:42:23,170
Even if perfect justice
is hard to seek in this world,

826
00:42:23,590 --> 00:42:25,650
one must not lose faith because of it,

827
00:42:25,740 --> 00:42:27,870
much less use it as an excuse to do evil.

828
00:42:28,280 --> 00:42:29,740
Only by upholding justice

829
00:42:30,100 --> 00:42:31,630
with a public-minded heart

830
00:42:32,150 --> 00:42:33,330
can we change

831
00:42:33,950 --> 00:42:35,590
this unfair world.

832
00:42:45,990 --> 00:42:48,430
If all officials were like Master Wan,

833
00:42:48,990 --> 00:42:50,320
all people under heaven

834
00:42:50,720 --> 00:42:52,780
could truly live in peace and safety.

